<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome Page</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Background Image with Faded Effect */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-image: url('/welcome-bg.jpg'); /* Make sure this image is inside the public folder */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            filter: brightness(50%); /* Adjust brightness for fading effect */
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(162, 159, 159, 0.7); /* Dark overlay effect */
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #344a35; /* Green for freshness */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: black;
        }

        .buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .btn {
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            color: white;
            background-color: #007BFF;
            transition: 0.3s ease-in-out, transform 1.2s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background-color: transparent;
            border: 2px solid white;
            transition: transform 1.2s;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>(‚óè'‚ó°'‚óè) Hey, Explore your Stocks Here! üìà</h1>
        <p>Welcome to our stock market platform. Start tracking your stocks today!</p>

        <div class="buttons">
            <a href="/signup" class="btn">Sign Up</a>
            <a href="/signin" class="btn btn-outline">Sign In</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
